title: Aaron Rodgers, Dak Prescott, Steelers, & QB rankings
itunes:title: Aaron Rodgers, Dak Prescott, Steelers, & QB rankings
description:
Colin discusses the Green Bay Packers, their match up with the Philadelphia Eagles, and QB Aaron Rodgers' comments. Colin believes the Dallas Cowboys waited too long and will have to overpay for QB Dak Prescott, why he thinks there is still hope for the Pittsburgh Steelers, and his thoughts on Pro Football Focus' QB rankings. Guests include Nick Wright, Al Michaels, Jordan Palmer, and Shawn Porter.
